Title : Cayla Kluver
Text : '''Cayla Kluver''' is an American author known for her [[Young adult literature|young adult]] trilogy series  ''[[Legacy (novel series)|Legacy]]'', which she began writing while she was fourteen.<ref>{{cite web|title=Llega "Legacy", la novela fantástica que lanzó a la fama mundial a Cayla Kluver|url=http://www.emol.com/noticias/magazine/2010/09/13/435858/llega-legacy-la-novela-fantastica-que-lanzo-a-la-fama-mundial-a-cayla-kluver.html|publisher=Emol|accessdate=27 January 2013}}</ref> Kluver originally self-published the series before it was picked up by [[AmazonEncore]] and later, [[Harlequin Teen]].<ref name="auto">{{cite web|title=Accomplished first-year Cayla Kluver working on fourth book|url=http://www.etownian.com/features/accomplished-first-year-cayla-kluver-working-on-fourth-book/|publisher=Etownian|accessdate=27 January 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Amazon Launches Publishing Program|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/industry-news/publisher-news/article/4995-amazon-launches-publishing-program.html|publisher=Publishers Weekly|accessdate=27 January 2013}}</ref> Kluver briefly attended [[Elizabethtown College]] for one year.<ref name="auto"/> Kluver lives in [[Eau Claire, Wisconsin]].

